"583258660791828", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974679_583258664125161_3421990995910339195_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=GhBM12lqpo8Q7kNvgHo-zKT&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDX4r3YZhyE154NtY81jftg9fk7zsWO0jWfrCf2Bqh2FA&oe=6745B4E9"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "main2560_1440-01.png", "id": "1563049480955863", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031607_1563049484289196_8523769749790803732_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KqniW06pSHEQ7kNvgHwtjZW&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDbYj6z87erAqbo5Iv5rqvHk1eK1rJyp_fDxfk7HerHwg&oe=6745A9AA"}, "display_name": "UniMed+ solfeggio with VR", "keywords": ["meditation", "therapy", "solfeggio", "mindfulness", "yoga"], "long_description": "\"Unlock Your Inner Peace with UniMed+.\n\nDive into a transformative journey with our meditation app that harnesses the power of Solfeggio frequencies. Designed for both beginners and seasoned meditators, our app offers a unique experience to elevate your mindfulness practice.\n\nFeatures:\nSolfeggio Mixer.\nBGM Mixer.\nBGM uses spatial audio (3D sound) technology.\nSpatial audio creates an immersive experience by simulating sounds from all directions: above, below, around, behind you.\n\nWhy Solfeggio Frequencies?\nThese ancient sound frequencies are believed to promote healing, balance, and spiritual growth. Each tone resonates with different aspects of your well-being, helping you achieve deeper relaxation and focus.\"", "short_description": "\"Unlock Your Inner Peace with UniMed+.\n\nDive into a transformative journey with our meditation app that harnesses the power of Solfeggio frequencies. Designed for both beginners and seasoned meditators, our app offers a unique experience to elevate your mindfulness practice."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sbluedot1.wixsite.com/bluedot-stud